---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Flora Endless Word Search"
  description="A relaxing endless word search game for iPhone and iPad."
>
  <section class="page-hero container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Flora Endless Word Search</p>
    <h1>Relaxing word search puzzles, designed for everyone.</h1>
    <p>
      Flora is a simple, calming word search experience with endless categories,
      progress tracking, and accessibility-first design.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="content-card">
    <img
      src="/icons/flora.png"
      alt="Flora Endless Word Search app icon"
      width="120"
      height="120"
      class="app-icon"
    />

    <h2>About Flora</h2>
    <p>
      Flora Endless Word Search is built for players who enjoy calm, familiar,
      and easy-to-use word search puzzles. The app creates new puzzles across
      different themes and keeps track of your completed puzzles, words found,
      and streaks.
    </p>

    <h2>Features</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Endless word search puzzles</li>
      <li>Multiple word categories</li>
      <li>Progress and statistics tracking</li>
      <li>Dark Mode support</li>
      <li>Dynamic Type support</li>
      <li>VoiceOver-friendly labels</li>
      <li>Designed for iPhone and iPad</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Privacy</h2>
    <p>
      Flora is designed with privacy in mind. The current version does not
      collect personal information, show ads, track users, or require an account.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="/privacy/flora">View Flora Privacy Policy →</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Status</h2>
    <p>
      Flora Endless Word Search is currently preparing for App Store release.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>